p2: EXPENDITURE RESULTING FROM GENERAL FUNCTIONS CARRIED OUT BY THE INSTITUTION
p22: EXPENSES RELATING TO THE OMBUDSMAN’S DUTIES
p222: Expenses relating to the Ombudsman’s duties
p3: This appropriation is intended to cover expenditure incurred owing to the special nature of the Ombudsman’s duties such as relations with the national ombudsmen and international organisations of ombudsmen and subscriptions to international organisations.
